Description:
This chamber is full of devices intended to extract blood and has a great hole in the middle, whose purpose escapes your knowledge, but you can feel magical energies emanating from it. The room also has some space designed to host a small garrison.

The guards of this garrison react to your presence and ask if you are here to participate in the blood exchange experiment. 

You don’t know what they are talking about, but if they intend to use those devices on you, it will probably hurt, although it may be a good chance to access the hole's energy.
